{"tid":398764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩歲已識加減乘除 港數學神童13歲讀碩士","createTime":"2017-09-13T12:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T13:22:47.000Z","uid":64694,"like":118,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb778434b0d3afd1882b4ea659cf0867d245233e","tid":398764,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】香港再誕生數學神童，由香港移民到蘇格蘭的羅宏博（Lo Wang Pok），以13歲之齡完成英國公開大學（Open University）的數學學士學位課程，並以一級榮譽畢業，他會以兼讀形式在雪菲爾大學（Sheffield University）修讀統計與醫療應用碩士。<br />\n<br />\n羅宏博表示，十分開心可以一級榮譽畢業，「我很享受學習數學，但也越來越有挑戰性，數理概念開始越來越難和抽象，主要是靠邏輯和推理。」雖然年紀輕輕已在大學以一級榮譽畢業，但羅宏博仍有在傳統學校就讀，閒時喜歡與朋友外出，鐘情彈鋼琴和結他。<br />\n<br />\n羅宏博2006年由香港移民到蘇格蘭，兩歲已懂得加減乘除並展現出數學天份，11歲就通過數學科高級程度考試並取得「A」級成績。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E6%AD%B2%E5%B7%B2%E8%AD%98%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%9B%E4%B9%98%E9%99%A4-%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%B8%E7%A5%9E%E7%AB%A513%E6%AD%B2%E8%AE%80%E7%A2%A9%E5%A3%AB-081600869.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E8%25AD%2598%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B8%259B%25E4%25B9%2598%25E9%2599%25A4-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25AB%25A513%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%25AE%2580%25E7%25A2%25A9%25E5%25A3%25AB-081600869.html&d=K%2BrjvxT0%2FZuN7sZZp0RS3DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=95ac5f66\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E6%AD%B2%E5%B7%B2%E8%AD%98%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%9B%E4%B9%98%E9%99%A4-%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%B8%E7%A5%9E%E7%AB%A513%E6%AD%B2%E8%AE%80%E7%A2%A9%E5%A3%AB-081600869.html</a>"},{"pid":"efbfa0823854c3f9962865066fa3caa8057949e5","tid":398764,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b26fa533455e1e8431126455918ed4d0144476","tid":398764,"uid":1267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:14:27.000Z","msg":"如果冇移民嘅話<img src=\"/assets/fa